node.text: [Famous Amos] - you just can’t go wrong with @famousamossg cookies. Stocking up and I can snack anything.
@jooooostina hahhahaaa remember to have your salt water ready
@sgfoodonfoot 😆🤣🤣 no, I got something better. Coconut water, baby! ✌🏻
Very dangerous to leave Famous Amos cookies with me. Sure finish all in less than a day 😆
